Put all ``.ipynb`` notebooks here.

The ``Makefiles`` in ``characters``, ``items``, and ``spells`` will 
extract the definitions from these notebooks to create Python modules.

The modules will then produce the RST files (with extensions ``.txt``) 
for final publication.

The manually-created RST files will have an extension of ``.rst`` to make
it clear which files are part of the main outline.
The ``.txt`` files will be brought into the document with ``..  include::`` directives.
